    "description": "这是一款类暗黑的RPG刷宝游戏，游戏在箱庭式的地图中进行，玩家需要击败怪物，收集其掉落的道具，并通过词缀组合，搭配出自己需要的道具，道具与词缀的收集与组合是游戏的主要玩法<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>将道具，装备，技能融为一体，统称为道具，更加简单，上手更快。道具拥有表演时间，表演时间内技能无限释放。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/58e3e6b81819376fa5b39a848a746ebf.poster.avif?t=1681444820\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/58e3e6b81819376fa5b39a848a746ebf.webm?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/58e3e6b81819376fa5b39a848a746ebf.mp4?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>道具随意编辑，道具上的词缀可随意交换组合。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/265dcbf8a39cee577523034180d6c7eb.poster.avif?t=1681444820\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/265dcbf8a39cee577523034180d6c7eb.webm?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/265dcbf8a39cee577523034180d6c7eb.mp4?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>通过词缀组合，得到更强力的技能，或者提升巨量属性值，这一切都由玩家自己选择。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/b7ecc382712928fe9ec0db5b53955d2b.poster.avif?t=1681444820\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/b7ecc382712928fe9ec0db5b53955d2b.webm?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/b7ecc382712928fe9ec0db5b53955d2b.mp4?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>加入思维输出系统，可以改变任意物体的AI逻辑。也可以改变物体阵营，将他们解锁为可操作角色，不同的角色拥有不同的成长率，去收集强力BOSS吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/e86230e80638468de91af2e9e15a0990.poster.avif?t=1681444820\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/e86230e80638468de91af2e9e15a0990.webm?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2260850/extras/e86230e80638468de91af2e9e15a0990.mp4?t=1681444820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
